{"tid":2276920,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓網超火爆選擇題：2億年薪 VS 8000萬年薪要怎麼選？當然還有附加條件！","createTime":"2020-11-08T06:16:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T12:06:39.000Z","uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"f403be859b74cedd573c836edf01218e95427396","tid":2276920,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:16:44.000Z","msg":"雖然我們還沒有擁有，但不妨礙我們做做白日夢，畢竟夢想一定要有，萬一實現了呢?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最近韓網上超火的選擇題是什麼呢? 2億年薪VS8000萬年薪+賓士，引來超多人的回復，看來無論哪國人，都有個暴富的白日夢啊，哈哈哈~<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nA選項是年薪2億，無論你做什麼工作都能賺夠2個億，但付出的代價就是無法擁有夢寐以求的車，哪怕是小型轎車都不行，唯一可以擁有的就是一輛小卡車，且出行工具也是這輛車。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_10dd110dfd22ea67acd9cfe7551dbe4f/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-05/131433-883474.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_10dd110dfd22ea67acd9cfe7551dbe4f%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-05%2F131433-883474.png&h=e3545766&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_5c402febd3df76410114083c20f3d0d3/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-05/131433-883475.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_5c402febd3df76410114083c20f3d0d3%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-05%2F131433-883475.png&h=5e1d6fd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nB選項則是年薪8000萬，但卻能擁有讓無數人羨慕的豪華座駕-最新款的Benz。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_93f4c6594b183dc9038aa399ee954d59/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-05/131433-883476.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_93f4c6594b183dc9038aa399ee954d59%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-05%2F131433-883476.png&h=30b55431&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_d5d878513767e42771ec58d8d94f06ab/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-05/131433-883477.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_d5d878513767e42771ec58d8d94f06ab%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-05%2F131433-883477.png&h=d05e3a7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而無論你選擇哪一項，你的錢都不能用來買車，外出使用的交通工具也只能是A、B選項中的兩種，要麼是小卡車，要麼是Benz，飛機、火車、的士通通不行。有不少人選A，覺得：「有錢最重要，做什麼車無所謂」、「年薪都2億了，還要什麼車」、「給我年薪2億，我可以走路去」。 也有很多人選B，認為：「坐上Benz才能昂首挺胸啊」、「其實8000萬也夠了」、「小卡車要一類駕照，考起來太麻煩了」等。<br />\n<br />\n那麼，你的選擇是什麼呢?<br />\n<br />\n「圖：NATE PHOTOS」"},{"pid":"9047785d23e5a73208239345dadc73579f3cf6f7","tid":2276920,"uid":167464,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:17:49.000Z","msg":"叫uber得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"754b557f78673ece2c8f26792bf0f9945344b565","tid":2276920,"uid":15371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9047785d23e5a73208239345dadc73579f3cf6f7","tid":2276920,"uid":167464,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:17:49.000Z","msg":"叫uber得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:20:46.000Z","msg":"的士 uber都唔得"},{"pid":"5930253569d3f433af1add6656e9aca7b72a3315","tid":2276920,"uid":15371,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:21:23.000Z","msg":"兩樣都唔揀<br />\n繼續做電競選手<br />\n公司有車接送<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be767b26327077d0bf8290812e98e004c898741","tid":2276920,"uid":71847,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:21:54.000Z","msg":"韓國年薪2億 無話好多 香港中產"},{"pid":"8d77090fe5e40529538444241aa44f35f2fccfcb","tid":2276920,"uid":83648,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"9be767b26327077d0bf8290812e98e004c898741","tid":2276920,"uid":71847,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:21:54.000Z","msg":"韓國年薪2億 無話好多 香港中產"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:23:43.000Z","msg":"即係幾多"},{"pid":"9517c8998587f153494e1387a21031764edde945","tid":2276920,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5930253569d3f433af1add6656e9aca7b72a3315"